metadata.name: Aus DeFi NFT Heroes - Enthusiast #1/33
metadata.description: He lives for the good vibes! He has a background in social media and events management. He once held down 27 different Discord community manager roles, simultaneously. Heâ€™s aped into more NFT projects than we can count. He will try anything new. He has a Kepler wallet, Rainbow, Zerion, Phantom, SenGo, MarcoPolo, Trust, Trezor, Ledger, Argent, DefiSwap and of course, Metamask. He can recite the Bitcoin whitepaper from start to finish, as a party trick. He comes to every Aus DeFi Meetup, even travelling interstate to say hi in every city. He has a collection of branded crypto merch tee shirts, now numbering about 69. Always first to ask questions on a webinar, this guy. He has an uncanny knack for knowing everyone in a room. And we simply cannot find anyone who dislikes him. Maybe that enthusiasm really is infectious?
